{"tid":1612130,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個階段除左勇武抗爭之外，臨時議會(已成立)應該多一點重視同討論","createTime":"2019-10-02T07:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:32:35.000Z","uid":31215,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4be7d4ee18310f29a14617941f760bd53f3f6387","tid":1612130,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:07:11.000Z","msg":"辛灝年講得幾好<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kjPzht_pgCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkjPzht_pgCQ&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=a33f28e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kjPzht_pgCQ</a><br />\n<br />\n而家唔係求你改良，求你俾權我<br />\n個權我本身都有<br />\n你唔想俾都要俾<br />\n而迫佢正視民權嘅方法就係透個搞好臨時議會<br />\n27:00<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理的建立人民議會<br />\n勇武的保護人民議會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要迫政府重視人民議會<br />\n社會嘅大小議題都會經人民議會討論同表決<br />\n如果個冇認受性嘅立法會敢過惡法，無視同踐踏人民議會<br />\n人民議會就號召市民激烈反抗，保衛人民議會尊嚴<br />\n自此立法會所有議案都有人民議會監察，一違背民意就引發反送中程度示威<br />\n從此政府除左要顧立法會夠唔夠票之外，都要顧埋人民議會嘅反應<br />\n<br />\n而人民議會一定要有一個規則<br />\n20:00<br />\n任何人都不得點名/提名任何一個人去擔任議員<br />\n一定要由下而上，由最底層嘅人選出黎 (小弟我覺得代議士都唔需要)<br />\n17:39<br />\n如果由上往下，各種干涉就會黎，各種不同性質名人就會黎，各種跟中共或某黨某黨有關係嘅人都會黎，各種認為自己好有名氣嘅人都會黎，會令呢個議會喺某程度同某時候轉眼就成為唔係人民嘅議會<br />\n<br />\n結論: <br />\n我地一邊爭雙普選，成功之前一邊自己搞臨時議會監察立法會，有咩大小議案我地自己先傾一次，係惡法就反佢枱<br />\n同時警剔個組成一定要由下而上，就算成立嗰班人都冇得代表人，冇得指下個鼻撻朵就佔一席位叫人聽佢支笛，底層，即係廣大市民睇法先係最重要<br />\n<br />\n認同請加入連登仔整嘅議會雛形<br />\ntg: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkpporganizationchannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpporganizationchannel&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=a890ed66\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkpporganizationchannel</a><br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1606510/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1606510/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9e2ba2b40da746e4fcb66e75794f07744a278c","tid":1612130,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:10:40.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"340a24f44e09cfe347aa0d72c8227d6cb1f8c68c","tid":1612130,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:14:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a930759b7c981afa58ae93bca372045d3ce788","tid":1612130,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:15:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌佢老母啦<br />\n臨議會乜聲都冇<br />\n喂你成立左唔做野同我係屋企搞獨立有乜野分別</span>"},{"pid":"bab1c537812cd301df1fea802664be2c01998f8f","tid":1612130,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n@hkpp_qna_bot<br />\n<br />\n炸撚爆佢個tg<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3beedc9b29426c533795ff21acb54dd6441d3516","tid":1612130,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30a930759b7c981afa58ae93bca372045d3ce788","tid":1612130,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:15:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌佢老母啦<br />\n臨議會乜聲都冇<br />\n喂你成立左唔做野同我係屋企搞獨立有乜野分別</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"都冇人重視<br />\n人又唔夠<br />\n投票又得嗰少少人"},{"pid":"3ffc7d13f1b9fe1f7efbdea6976c0f329efa25f9","tid":1612130,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3beedc9b29426c533795ff21acb54dd6441d3516","tid":1612130,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30a930759b7c981afa58ae93bca372045d3ce788","tid":1612130,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:15:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌佢老母啦<br />\n臨議會乜聲都冇<br />\n